#. module: billboard_rental
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:billboard_rental.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<span class=\"oe-tabs\" style=\"width: 40px;\"> </span>​But others are "
"looking for guidance. In that case, they book a meeting"
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"oe-tabs\" style=\"width: 40px;\"> </span>​ແຕ່ບາງຄົນກໍ່ກຳລັງຊອກຫາຄຳແນະ"
"ນຳ. ໃນກໍລະນີນັ້ນ, ພວກເຂົາຈະຈອງການປະຊຸມ"

#. module: billboard_rental
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:billboard_rental.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<span class=\"oe-tabs\" style=\"width: 40px;\"> </span>​From there, an Opportunity is created in the the CRM and a salesperson is assigned to that request.<br/>\n"
"                    <span class=\"oe-tabs\" style=\"width: 40px;\"> </span>​After some preliminary discussions, the lead will move to the Territory Research stage, where the salesperson <span class=\"oe-tabs\" style=\"width: 1.28333px;\"> </span>​will perform some\n"
"                    analysis to see which of the available billboard_rental is best for their campaign"
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"oe-tabs\" style=\"width: 40px;\"> </span>​ຈາກນັ້ນ, ໂອກາດຈະຖືກສ້າງຂຶ້ນໃ"
"ນ CRM ແລະ ພະນັກງານຂາຍຈະຖືກມອບໝາຍໃຫ້ກັບຄໍາຮ້ອງຂໍນັ້ນ.<br/>\n"
"                    <span class=\"oe-tabs\" style=\"width: 40px;\"> </span>​ຫຼັງ"
"ຈາກການປຶກສາຫາລືເບື້ອງຕົ້ນ, ລູກຄ້າເປົ້າໝາຍຈະຍ້າຍໄປສູ່ຂັ້ນຕອນການຄົ້ນຄວ້າເຂດພື້ນທີ່, ເຊິ່ງພະນັກງານຂາຍ "
"<span class=\"oe-tabs\" style=\"width: 1.28333px;\"> </span>​ຈະເຮັດການວິເຄາະບາງຢ່"
"າງ\n"
"                    ເພື່ອເບິ່ງວ່າປ້າຍໂຄສະນາໃດທີ່ມີວ່າງຢູ່ ແລະ ເໝາະສົມທີ່ສຸດສຳລັບແຄມເປນຂອງພວກເຂົ"
"າ"

#. module: billboard_rental
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:billboard_rental.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<span class=\"oe-tabs\" style=\"width: 40px;\"> </span>​Further down the "
"process a Quotation is created. This is where the available Billboard will "
"be selected.<br/>"
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"oe-tabs\" style=\"width: 40px;\"> </span>​ໃນຂັ້ນຕອນຕໍ່ໄປ, ໃບສະເໜີລາຄາ"
"ຈະຖືກສ້າງຂຶ້ນ. ນີ້ແມ່ນບ່ອນທີ່ຈະເລືອກປ້າຍໂຄສະນາທີ່ວ່າງຢູ່.<br/>"

#. module: billboard_rental
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:billboard_rental.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<span class=\"oe-tabs\" style=\"width: 40px;\"> </span>​It is also at this "
"point that one needs to decide which kind of subscription to use (short or "
"long term)."
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"oe-tabs\" style=\"width: 40px;\"> </span>​ມັນຍັງເປັນຈຸດນີ້ທີ່ຕ້ອງຕັດສິນໃຈວ່າ"
"ຈະໃຊ້ການສະໝັກແບບໃດ (ໄລຍະສັ້ນ ຫຼື ໄລຍະຍາວ)."

#. module: billboard_rental
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:billboard_rental.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<span class=\"oe-tabs\" style=\"width: 40px;\"> </span>​The company handles two kinds of leads.<br/>\n"
"                    <br/>\n"
"                    <span class=\"oe-tabs\" style=\"width: 40px;\"> </span>​First, they get requests from customers that want a specific billboard_rental, for example because they saw it in the <span class=\"oe-tabs\" style=\"width: 15.3px;\"> </span>​streets. For those\n"
"                    a lead is created manually, directly in the CRM, while the prospect is on the phone."
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"oe-tabs\" style=\"width: 40px;\"> </span>​ບໍລິສັດຈັດການກັບລູກຄ້າເປົ້າໝາຍສ"
"ອງປະເພດ.<br/>\n"
"                    <br/>\n"
"                    <span class=\"oe-tabs\" style=\"width: 40px;\"> </span>​ທຳ"
"ອິດ, ພວກເຂົາໄດ້ຮັບຄຳຮ້ອງຂໍຈາກລູກຄ້າທີ່ຕ້ອງການປ້າຍໂຄສະນາສະເພາະໃດໜຶ່ງ, ຕົວຢ່າງຍ້ອນວ່າພວກເຂົາເຫັນມັນຢູ່"
"ຕາມ <span class=\"oe-tabs\" style=\"width: 15.3px;\"> </span>​ທ້ອງຖະໜົນ. ສຳລັບກໍລະ"
"ນີເຫຼົ່ານັ້ນ\n"
"                    ລູກຄ້າເປົ້າໝາຍຈະຖືກສ້າງຂຶ້ນດ້ວຍຕົນເອງໂດຍກົງໃນ CRM ໃນຂະນະທີ່ກຳລັງລົມໂທລະສັ"
"ບກັບລູກຄ້າ."

#. module: billboard_rental
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:billboard_rental.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<span class=\"oe-tabs\" style=\"width: 40px;\"> </span>​To quickly encode "
"the orders, salespersons use Quotation Templates, that already contain the "
"basic packages."
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"oe-tabs\" style=\"width: 40px;\"> </span>​ເພື່ອບັນທຶກຄໍາສັ່ງຊື້ຢ່າງວ່ອງໄວ, "
"ພະນັກງານຂາຍຈະໃຊ້ແມ່ແບບໃບສະເໜີລາຄາທີ່ມີແພັກເກັດພື້ນຖານຢູ່ແລ້ວ."

